data.description: This house is waiting for the perfect family to call it home! This home is nestled in the highly sought after Warwick Addition. Imagine cooking holiday meals in the spacious kitchen that offers two ovens and the perfect island for prepping. This beautiful home sits at the end of a side street with a nice open space on the east side. Imagine the quietness from lack of street traffic! After walking through the entry way, a great size formal dining room sits off to the left. Walk past the formal dining and you’ll notice the living room that has large windows that allow for the perfect amount of natural light. The second living space (surprise!) is located off the kitchen. Use this space as an office, kids play area, or simply another room to entertain. This 4 bedroom/ 3 bath home is completely free of carpet and has enough space for everyone in the home to individualize. Large storm shelter in garage! If more space is needed, step out back to the spacious private backyard or simply across the grass to the neighborhood park! Come see this home with your own eyes before it sells!
